    <descriptions>
        <description descriptionType="Abstract">
            This dataset contains 50,000 music records with 14 features related to rhythm,
            loudness, vocal content, acoustic quality, energy, BPM, mood score,
            vibe score, and viral potential index. It is useful for music trend analysis,
            recommendation systems, and machine learning applications.
